{"tid":2220300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"反政府示威逮捕7000人 白俄外長轟外國干涉內政","createTime":"2020-09-27T14:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T12:35:52.000Z","uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"71a3b3ac730ac178c9b83b5a154840d59dfc96a9","tid":2220300,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:19:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ftvnews.com.tw/news/detail/2020927I10M1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ftvnews.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fdetail%2F2020927I10M1&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUkbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=6e9a1afc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ftvnews.com.tw/news/detail/2020927I10M1</a><br />\n白俄羅斯從8月初以來爆發反政府示威遭當局強力鎮壓，至今已有數名示威者喪命、多人受傷，還有近7000人被捕。昨天又有女性團體發起遊行，數十人遭逮。不過面對國內外譴責當局一概否認，白俄羅斯外長昨天在預錄好的聯合國大會發言中，更要他國別干預內政。<br />\n<br />\n蒙面鎮暴警高大魁梧，半拖半拉把人一個個抓進車子裡，無論旁人怎樣叫囂，都跟白俄當局一樣充耳未聞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimg.ftv.com.tw/summernotefiles/News/f9c351b4-2acd-4e44-b49b-c867444dc5a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimg.ftv.com.tw%2Fsummernotefiles%2FNews%2Ff9c351b4-2acd-4e44-b49b-c867444dc5a7.jpg&h=5a1c4243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白俄羅斯反政府示威持續7週，週末女性大遊行儼然成為常態。8月9日的大選，總統盧卡申科以8成得票率宣布第六次連任，選前呼聲最高的反對黨候選人季哈諾夫斯卡婭，最終竟只拿下6.8%選票，登時民怨四起指控選舉不公，抗議民眾卻遭催淚煙橡膠子彈伺候，季哈諾夫斯卡婭也逃亡國外。不過面對國內反對派以及歐盟譴責，當局一概否認。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsimg.ftv.com.tw/summernotefiles/News/4a956a12-204c-45ad-8bce-7f70bda63b46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsimg.ftv.com.tw%2Fsummernotefiles%2FNews%2F4a956a12-204c-45ad-8bce-7f70bda63b46.jpg&h=d8d8a5b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外長甚至在聯大演說中，批判各國干涉內政。白俄羅斯外長馬克伊表示，「凡是干預我國內政或對白俄羅斯實施制裁或其他限令，都將招致反效果對所有人百害而無一利。」<br />\n<br />\n儘管反對聲浪高漲，盧卡申科依舊在23日低調宣誓就職，反對黨已揚言號召全國大規模串聯抗議。近來這波抗議活動，是白俄羅斯1991年自蘇聯獨立以來規模最大、持續最久的一次，首都明斯克一度有20萬人參與示威。"},{"pid":"6655c018eee3afbbc9dfc32041ad9dc5165953e9","tid":2220300,"uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:20:36.000Z","msg":"外國指俄羅斯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f381c4f776254213fd70d408dceb18352f0d19b","tid":2220300,"uid":107577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n借位宣傳行動post<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>[行動Post]十月一掛黑衫大行動</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2220323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2220323</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c5f2ac815def7c84e5505eacb17caf61db979317","tid":2220300,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T16:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a62c0ac0a03135f5a61462de782f5464ac4557","tid":2220300,"uid":55913,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T16:19:15.000Z","msg":"全世界既極權都係咁類似<br />\n當然有d玩放毒最仆街"},{"pid":"544b0cee149504c9deba99722129ac605f2c4778","tid":2220300,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T16:21:43.000Z","msg":"白俄=香港<br />\n俄羅斯=中共<br />\n<br />\n反抗者唔係面對表面幾萬警力<br />\n而係後面個大佬"},{"pid":"c2bc0da5b67aab55404d46e6b70fd5543189eda2","tid":2220300,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:22:12.000Z","msg":"其實點解外國示威 次次都咁容易就拉幾千人??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇番香港<br />\n黑警 次次玩大濫捕, 將路人/ 街坊 全部用幾架巴士帶走<br />\n但都要搞左一年先拉到七千人"},{"pid":"5c0a045a208a744811e45b2a5c666b4238ef9404","tid":2220300,"uid":23061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"條白羅傻鳩真係學足晒閪婆啲衰嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b01087ab8dd5a3ad0d3f6b054b2b9d30efba3a7","tid":2220300,"uid":172172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2bc0da5b67aab55404d46e6b70fd5